            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Sidera me retinent nil me <supplied reason="lost">mors impia terret</supplied> <lb n="2"/>ad vitam redii quae sine <supplied reason="lost">fine manet</supplied> <lb n="3"/>suscepi thalamos subolem fac<supplied reason="lost">tis monitura</supplied> <lb n="4"/>unum scisse virum virginis <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> diu <lb n="5"/>sunt dulcis natis <note>sic</note> superest gratusque maritus <lb n="6"/>nullos nosse dolos h<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ec</abbr></expan> mihi vita fuit </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Hic requiescit in pace in<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ustrissima</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>fem</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Decentia quae vixit annos <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>lus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> LXXVI deposita in pace <lb n="2"/>pridie <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Martias </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Hic requiescit in pace <expan><abbr>inl</abbr><ex>ustrissima</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fem</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Quypriana <note>sic</note> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> vixit annos <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>lus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> XLII deposita in pace <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>r<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ulatu</ex></expan> Volos<supplied reason="lost">iani! <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel ist in 12 Teile gebrochen. 3 Grabinschriften übereinander; obere Inschrift mit Zeilenlinien; Buchstabenhöhe der beiden unteren Inschriften: 1,5-2,5 cm. Z. 10 (Anfang): Reste zweier überstrichener Zahlzeichen sowie zweier nicht mehr identifizierbarer Buchstaben.</p>
